{
  "stem": "4189.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes the bread was so fresh that it would fall apart.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You couldn't really divide it properly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When you would break it, it would fall apart.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So these were the conditions that we had to live under.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Besides this bread, each one had a bowl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was your bowl.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that bowl would give you-- every day they would give you 1 liter of so-called soup.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And also with the bread, they would give you a small portion of margarine, a tiny little slab like when you go to a restaurant and they give you those little pieces of butter.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, on that order like that, that was the daily ration.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they would give you tea, which was sometimes couldn't drink it because it was so bitter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That tea was made from herbs, because they had no regular tea.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And of course coffee was unheard of in Auschwitz and in Germany, because coffee came from Brazil.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the war was on, there was no coffee anywhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So that's-- that was our ration.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So to survive under those conditions was practically impossible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They wanted to kill us, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That was their aim.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They wanted to annihilate us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The people that went straight to the gas chamber when they arrived were better off than we were at that time in the camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Even though they needed us to work, they were working us till we dropped, because when anybody dropped, we had to pick them up, bring them back to the camp to be counted again.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because every day when we came back from work we had to line up in groups, each block, which was about 1,000 people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And in Auschwitz itself were approximately 24,000 to 25,000 prisoners in that main camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
